# 5. Business Requirements

## ROLE-001

Every authenticated user must be assigned at least one role.

A user without a role cannot access the platform.

---

## ROLE-002

Permissions are granted through roles.

Permissions are never assigned directly to users.

---

## ROLE-003

A user may be assigned multiple roles.

Effective permissions are the union of all assigned roles.

---

## ROLE-004

System roles are protected.

System roles cannot be deleted.

---

## ROLE-005

The system shall provide default roles including:

* Firm Owner
* Firm Administrator
* Attorney
* Paralegal
* Staff

Additional roles may be created by authorized users.

---

## ROLE-006

Every permission belongs to exactly one permission group.

---

## ROLE-007

Permission evaluation must always occur on the backend.

The frontend may hide functionality for usability purposes only.

---

## ROLE-008

Authorization decisions must be evaluated for every protected API request.

---

## ROLE-009

Role changes become effective immediately.

New permissions apply without requiring user intervention other than re-evaluation of authorization.

---

## ROLE-010

Permission changes must never modify historical business records.

---

## ROLE-011

Every role assignment and permission change must be recorded by the Audit Log module.

---

## ROLE-012

Modules must never implement their own authorization logic.

Every module must use this centralized authorization system.

---

# 6. User Stories

### Create Role

As a Firm Administrator,

I want to create custom roles,

so I can control access for my staff.

---

### Edit Role

As a Firm Administrator,

I want to modify role permissions,

so responsibilities can evolve over time.

---

### Assign Role

As a Firm Administrator,

I want to assign roles to users,

so they receive the correct permissions.

---

### View Roles

As a Firm Administrator,

I want to view all available roles,

so I can manage firm security.

---

### Evaluate Permission

As the system,

I want to evaluate user permissions,

before allowing protected operations.

---

### Remove Role

As a Firm Administrator,

I want to remove unused custom roles,

without affecting system roles.

