# 8. Data Model

This module follows the standards defined in:

* 003 - Database Conventions

This module owns the following collections.

| Collection       | Purpose                                  |
| ---------------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| roles            | Defines user roles within a firm         |
| permissions      | Defines all available system permissions |
| role_permissions | Maps permissions to roles                |
| user_roles       | Maps users to roles                      |

